sition":0},"title":"Hadith on Umrah: Two pilgrimages rewarded with forgiveness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe 'Umrah pilgrimage to the following 'Umrah will expiate whatever sins were committed between them, and the blessed Hajj pilgrimage has no reward other than Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1773, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1349 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18530,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/15\/hajj-umrah-cut-shave-head\/","url_meta":{"origin":15610,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Recommendation to shave head, permission to cut only","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: At the end of the Hajj pilgrimage, the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, have mercy upon those who shaved their heads.\u201d They said, \u201cAnd those who cut their hair short, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cO Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15510,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/dua-returning-hajj-umrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15610,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Supplication for returning home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, whenever he returned from the armies, campaigns, Hajj, or \u2018Umrah, he would exalt Allah three times at the top of every hill or plateau. Then, the Prophet would say, \u201cThere is no God but Allah alone,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/13\/when-a-hajji-dies-talbiya\/","url_meta":{"origin":15610,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: When someone dies while on the pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man performing the pilgrimage was thrown from his camel and died while we were with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u00a0The Prophet said, \u201cWash him with water mixed with the leaves of a lote tree and shroud him in his two garments. Do not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2084,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/17\/five-pillars-of-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":15610,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Religion of Islam is built on five pillars","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIslam is built upon five: to worship Allah and to disbelieve in what is worshiped besides Him, to establish prayer, to give charity, to perform the Hajj pilgrimage to the house, and to fast the month\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Featured&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Featured","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/featured\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31722,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/talbiyah-hajj-pilgrimage\/","url_meta":{"origin":15610,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Talbiyah: Responding to the call of Hajj pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would answer the call of the pilgrimage, saying, \u201cI am here at Your service, O Allah, at Your service! I am here at Your service, You have no partner! I am here at Your service! Verily,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15610","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15610"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/po